                    <h1>Single Layer Flexible PCB for Simple, Bendable Interconnects</h1>
                    <p class="service-lead">XFPCB builds single layer flexible PCBs for lightweight interconnects, sensor tails, display links and compact electronic products.</p>
                    <div class="service-actions"><a class="service-primary" href="#quote">Request a Quote</a><a class="service-secondary" href="/support/">Ask Technical Support</a></div>
